# zkSync Project

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![zkSync](https://img.shields.io/badge/built%20with-zkSync-4E76A8)](https://zksync.io/)

## Overview

This project showcases various functionalities and use cases related to zkSync, a layer-2 scaling solution for Ethereum.

