## Prerequisites

Make sure you have the following prerequisites installed:

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)
- [Truffle](https://www.trufflesuite.com/truffle)
- [zkSync SDK](https://github.com/matter-labs/zksync)

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/zksync-project.git

# Change directory
cd zksync-project

# Install dependencies
npm install
